Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.05,0:00:03.05,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}As bright as a spark,\Nwith a penetratingly precise wit.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.05,0:00:04.75,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Once he gets started, you can't stop him!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.75,0:00:06.49,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Today we solve the mystery of the legend!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.49,0:00:08.73,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}The trick and the evidence\Nare beyond your imagination!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.73,0:00:10.45,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}He sees the single truth for what it is,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.45,0:00:12.45,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}and looks like a kid but has the mind of an adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.45,0:00:15.04,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}His name? Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.16,0:01:39.86,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}We came to an old temple with a five-story pagoda while on vacation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.28,0:01:47.08,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}But development of a tourist attraction has brought trouble with the tour company.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.17,0:01:52.21,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}And the next morning, the president of the tour company, Hideaki Oda,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:55.18,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}was found hanging from the pagoda.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.03,0:01:59.44,Narration,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Exactly like the legend surrounding the pagoda...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.12,0:02:02.68,Dialogue,,0000,0000,0000,,It's the curse!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.40,0:02:04.72,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}Now I'm sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.72,0:02:06.72,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}This is the true crime scene!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.90,0:02:09.71,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}If my deduction is right,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.97,0:02:13.06,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}then Oda-{\i1}san{\i0} didn't kill himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.80,0:02:14.75,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}He was murdered!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.33,0:02:20.71,Thoughts,,0000,0000,0000,,{\blur2}And the one who did it was him,\Nthe one who said {\i1}that{\i0} back then!
